  "title": "LAST MILE DELIVERY DRIVER (VAN)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Delivery goods and parcel delivery</li>\n  <li>Perform safety checks before driving off</li>\n  <li>Ensure the vehicle is in a condition for safe operation by performing daily checks on the vehicle before the start of each working day</li>\n  <li>Good service to customers</li>\n  <li>Verify the contents of inventory loads against shipping papers</li>\n  <li>Any other adhoc duties/task assigned by superior</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Class 3 driving license with 2 years minimum prior license issuance</li>\n  <li>2 to 3 years’ experience in pick up, delivery. Pick up experience is an advantage</li>\n  <li>Able to work independently and be part of a team</li>\n  <li>Self-motivated and thrives in a fast-growing and dynamic environment</li>\n  <li>Ability to deliver under tight deadline</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>",
